snippet.title: Rocket League Season 4 Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Rocket League Season 4 Cinematic Trailer! Visit https://www.rocketleague.com/season-4/ for more details.

Saddle up for the rootinest tootinest season of Rocket League yet! Wrangle up your posse and hit the dusty trail for Rocket League Season 4! There's trouble brewin' in the newest Arena, Deadeye Canyon. Outlaw, the car that's new around these parts, is wanted demoed or intact. Capture it in the all-new Season 4 Rocket Pass, plus unlock the fanciest provisions in the 70+ Tiers of new items! 

Meet at high noon, win your duels, and become a tall tale in the Competitive Ranks. Complete weekly and Season Challenges to receive bounties of XP and Items. Join Tournaments with your crew, including the newly added 2v2 and Extra Mode Tournaments! 

See you on the prairie starting August 11!

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSeason4 #RocketLeagueTrailer
